(456, 'AI notes: ### Fund Backgrounds and Structure ### Investment Strategy ### Portfolio Companies ### Future Plans ### Action Items
RM notes: 1. Groww founders invested through Stargazer LLP since 2020 1. 60 investments to date 1. Small cheques 1. Mehta Family was the first investor in Groww 1. This is a CAT 2 AIF - Mehta Equities was the investment manager 1. Got license in 2023 1. ₹70 crore Fund I 1. 39 companies invested to date 1. Early cheques were ₹15L 1. Now doing ₹5 crore cheques 1. Thesis 1. Not tied down to BFSI - sector agnostic 1. Consumer (FirstClub, Zepto, Swiggy, Handpickd, Gaming, Caava, Bold Care) 1. FinTech (excluding Wealth, Lending) - keen on Infra & compliance - PowerEdge, Decentro  etc 1. AI - OnFinance, Snowmountain AI, Maxim AI 1. Have done some Pre-IPO as well 1. Lots of investments in common with DeVC Fund I 1. Cybrilla 1. Finsire 1. Riverline 1. PowerEdge 1. Snowmountain AI 1. Co’s he wants us to check out: 1. [https://www.revway.io/](https://www.revway.io/) 1. [https://babblebots.ai/](https://babblebots.ai/) 1. Fund II 1. TBD 1. Has been proposed 1. ₹120 crore CAT I AIF 1. Want to do more early stage (Seed to Series A) 1. Avoiding pre-IPO 1.
Action items: 1. Modus Secure - [https://www.modussecure.com/](https://www.modussecure.com/) 1. [https://portfolio.devc.com/](https://portfolio.devc.com/) 1. Someone to share a rough evaluation work?
