(466, 'Notes:: Spikey: non 0; <10% that this is a 1. Might surprise on upside given depth of early research he had come with and execution hustle (has 400 users already while building solo) Wants to build DevOps PaaS Render.com without a cloud lock in ; day 0 or whenever, customers can switch to own cloud. Have told him to think productized services like [https://www.percona.com](https://www.percona.com/) for mid market Notes from chat : Grew up in Bombay Undergrad was there Masters in US Tried a startup in 2009 - ed-tech Had a choice between Nykaa and Clevertap Why deployment Io ? AT Dezerv didn’t prioritise dev ops Felt that is the same at all cos Devops can be automated using AI Vision is to build an assistant for Devops and SRE for early teams They deploy on users AWS unlike render where when you scale you’d have to migrate Some kind of a PaaS experience on AWS Have around 300 users from 40 countries Wanted to build distribution first | currently all individual  developers Q to him : How do you solve distribution ? Easy to catch render type ICP ..but harder to solve distribution ? Two people right now. Full time is only Ankit. Another CT developer is part time Have built a Devops assistant too MLT becomes simple and chat based
